<trailer></trailer>
<names>
<name><ln>Gaff</ln><fn>William</fn><sf></sf><pf>Private</pf></name>;
<name><ln>Doyle</ln><fn>Isaac</fn><sf></sf><pf>Private</pf></name>;
<name><ln>Reynolds</ln><fn>Richard M.</fn><sf></sf><pf></pf></name>;
<name><ln>Reynolds</ln><fn></fn><sf></sf><pf>Dr.</pf></name>
</names>
<summary>Privates William Gaff and Isaac Doyle of Company A, 126th Reg't Penn. Volunteers,
have recently been honorably discharged from service on account of disability. Richard M.
